{"tid":1474567,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"冇警員編號/委任證既黑警，可否一律當冒警處理？良好市民幫手捉拿？","createTime":"2019-08-15T08:22:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T08:52:58.000Z","uid":29956,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"02971c1bb9b19bf8edc334a148470b37ff217751","tid":1474567,"uid":29956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:22:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">越黎越多不知名既&rdquo;警察&rdquo;，係冇證明自己身分既情況下執行暴力拘捕，作為良好市民，可否將冒警人士緝拿歸案？</span><br />\n<br />\n青年口面流血，沾滿一地，但另一名經過的防暴警察還未罷休，取出胡椒噴劑，近距離向他噴射；另一名卧底警員則從後按住他的雙腳。青年哭着道歉：「對唔住呀！唔好呀......」其間，防暴警察着同僚隔開記者，要求記者退後，「警察做緊嘢呀」、「圍住佢（青年）！推開佢哋（記者）」，數名正在拍攝的記者被阻擋鏡頭。<br />\n<br />\n不過，天網恢恢疏而不漏，過程被記者從後拍攝到，包括防暴警用警棍，向青年頭部猛毆兩次，<span style=\"color: red;\">而該名防暴警身上並沒有警員編號</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190815&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59935066\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190815%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59935066&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdqGgm0NOSfkDZSs230CVm%2Fs%3D&h=7ed94792\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190815%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59935066&h=2ac2440d\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190815&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59935066</a>"},{"pid":"5c93325458650cf1bd5845321e79bef35bcd7ea9","tid":1474567,"uid":29956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:23:59.000Z","msg":"黑警濫權"},{"pid":"428d4740f25c62fa4c31022302cf942c90aa29d8","tid":1474567,"uid":29956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:24:16.000Z","msg":"黑警濫權"},{"pid":"4281ca80a3984d131af72fe1f7890024af914dd5","tid":1474567,"uid":51234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:25:26.000Z","msg":"推呀，好多人都唔記得，屌哂你地咪立亂叫人做黑警，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>叫假警察呀</strong></span>，快啲洗自己腦，<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span s